Today, the Turkish-Azerbaijani Union is an indisputable factor in the world. Turkey's growing power also strengthens us.

The energy projects we have jointly strengthened us, new opportunities for our peoples, new business (cont) http://t.co/4LKSRuY9WS
Unfortunately, today is a dirty campaign against Turkey and Azerbaijan.
We respond to it with our own business. Today, it is difficult to find the second developing country in the world like Turkey and Azerbaijan.
Despite all the crises we are developing today. Our development is based on political will, historical truth.
TANAP is a energy security project.
Today, Shah Deniz is one of the world's largest gas fields and is currently the sole source of resources for the Southern Gas Corridor.
In the near future, gas will be extracted from other large gas fields of Azerbaijan and we will provide the Southern Gas Corridor with additional volumes.
At present, the work on the components of the Southern Gas Corridor is underway.
Today, the Southern Gas Corridor project is Europe's largest infrastructure project. This project will be launched (cont) http://t.co/jctd9WqW9o
The significance of the Southern Gas Corridor is that it is today in our region - Eurasia (cont) http://t.co/tj6Fki1jTj
The participating countries are becoming natural allies.
The Southern Gas Corridor is not just an energy project, it's a serious political initiative.
In the coming period, mutual understanding, coordination and mutual trust will accelerate our work.
All the projects we have so far put forth as initiatives jointly with Turkey and Georgia have succeeded.
I have no doubt that the Southern Gas Corridor and its important part, TANAP, will also be successful.
